FLASCHE
Copyright 2026 Kyung Hee University, Integrated Circuit Interface Lab

This repository accompanies the research work:
"FLASCHE: A Feedforward Location Activated Spike-based Computational-CAM
Hardening Edge-processor Using Hierarchical Feature Extraction for Rapid 
On-Chip Learning and Inference"

This repository contains:
- software code for CPU-based simulation and algorithm validation,
- hardware-related source code and supporting materials for implementation
  and verification.

